INUMBER 1908
NAME 847
ARMOR
WORN_DON
WEIGHT 1
VOLUME 1
IFPREVERB EXAMINE -1
  IFVAR INTNUM3 = 1
    ECHO PLAYER Chyme says, "This is Eliditur, only members of guild 22, or proven associates should have it. "
  ENDIF
  IFVAR ORG ! 22
    ECHO PLAYER ****ATTENTION**** this armband is now exclusively for Eliditur Members and associates, please destroy or assist to a gm to destroy if you do not belong to the Eliditur. Masquerade members see Sniffles about a replacement for your guild.*****
  ENDIF
ENDIF
IFTOUCH -1
  IFVAR ORG ! 22
    CLEARVERB
    ECHO PLAYER The armband begins glowing with an intense heat and you quickly snatch your hand away.
    ECHO OTHERS %N quickly snatches %h hand away from the glowing armband.
  ENDIF
ENDIF
IFPREVERB PUSH -1
  CLEARVERB
  IFVAR RNUM = 532
     ECHO GROUP You feel a slight tugging and then find yourself atop the crest of a large wave, your feet moving agilely over the surface of the water. You ride the wave for some time, always on the edge of disaster, before you spot the rocky shore of a small island. Guiding the wave perfectly you land on the shore and hear a voice inside your mind say, "Welcome home, Eliditur."
     ECHO OTHERS %P appears suddenly at a distance from the shore, riding along the top of a large wave. %P disappears slowly over the horizon of the Inner Sea.
     MOVEGROUP 2641
  ENDIF
  IFVAR RNUM = 2641
     ECHO GROUP You feel a slight tugging and then find yourself atop the crest of a large wave, your feet moving agilely over the surface of the water. You ride the wave for some time, always on the edge of disaster, before you spot the beaches of the Inner Sea. Guiding the wave perfectly you land on the beach and hear a voice inside your mind say, "Safe journey, Eliditur."
     ECHO OTHERS %P appears suddenly at a distance from the shoreline, riding along the top of a large wave. %P disappears slowly over the horizon headed towards the Inner Sea shore.
     MOVEGROUP 532
  ENDIF
ENDIF
IFPREVERB KISS -1
  CLEARVERB
  IFVAR RNUM = 532
     ECHO PLAYER You feel a slight tugging and then find yourself atop the crest of a large wave, your feet moving agilely over the surface of the water. You ride the wave for some time, always on the edge of disaster, before you spot the rocky shore of a small island. Guiding the wave perfectly you land on the shore and hear a voice inside your mind say, "Welcome home, Eliditur."
     ECHO OTHERS %N grips %h armband tightly, and steps out onto a rising wave. The winds blows through %h hair as %s rides the wave out to sea towards a faint mark on the horizon.
     MOVE 2641
  ENDIF
ENDIF
IFPREVERB LISTEN -1
  CLEARVERB
  ECHO PLAYER A shimmering blue field surrounds you, and you hear the whispered voices of the Eliditur that came before you preparing you for battle.
  ECHO OTHERS A shimmering blue field surrounds %N, full of a soft, sibilant voice that cannot be understood.
  IFVAR ITEMVAL5 ! DATE
    IFVAR ITEMVAL4 < 11
      ADD ITEMVAL4 1
      ECHO PLAYER A soft glow shimmers over your body, coming from the connection of your armband with the portal.
      SPELL 347 100
    ELSE
      EQUAL ITEMVAL5 DATE
      EQUAL ITEMVAL4 0
      ECHO PLAYER You sense the connection with the portal needs more time to recharge.
    ENDIF
  ELSE
    ECHO PLAYER You sense the connection with the portal needs more time to recharge.
  ENDIF 
ENDIF
IFPREVERB GESTURE -1
  CLEARVERB
  ECHO ALL A light slowly fills the area, coalescing into a shimmering rose that slowly fades from sight.
  PLREVENT 1
  CONTPLREVENT
  ECHO PLAYER In the center of the rose, a vision forms.
  SHOWROOM 2272
ENDIF
IFPREVERB CONCENTRATE -1
  CLEARVERB
  IFVAR ORG = 22
    ECHO ALL A crackling energy field bursts from overhead, bathing %N in its brilliant light.
    IFVAR ITEMVAL3 ! DATE
       ECHO PLAYER You feel a rush of mental and magical engeries infusing you from the connection of your armband with the portal! 
       ADD PSIPOINTS 200
       ADD MANAPOINTS 200
       EQUAL ITEMVAL3 DATE
    ELSE
       ECHO PLAYER You sense the connection with the portal needs more time to recharge.
    ENDIF
  ELSE
    ECHO ALL A small nimbus of blue energy crackles overhead, and bathes the face of %N in its soft light.
    IFVAR ITEMVAL3 ! DATE
      ECHO PLAYER You feel a rush of mental and magical engeries infusing you from the connection of your armband with the portal!
      ADD PSIPOINTS 100
      ADD MANAPOINTS 100
      EQUAL ITEMVAL3 DATE
    ELSE
      ECHO PLAYER  You sense the connection with the portal needs more time to recharge.
    ENDIF
  ENDIF
ENDIF
IFPREVERB SMELL -1
  CLEARVERB
  ECHO ALL The cloying scent of roses fills the air.
ENDIF
;
NUMBER 2641
NAME Eliditur Island, shore
ASTRAL
CALL 33
DAY_LIGHT
*DESCRIPTION_START
Large waves break against the rocky shores of this tiny, hidden island,
casting a fine mist over the area. The crash of the surf nearly drowns
out the faint sounds of wildlife that emanate from the small wooded
area a little further up the shore. The gently swaying trees brush their
leafy branches against the sides of a gleaming white tower. The tower
thrusts above the tree-line and reaches towards the sky. A marble arch
offers entry into the interior of the tower. 
*DESCRIPTION_END
ITEM 0 60 ADJ1=187 VAL2=2643
ITEM 1 80 VAL2=2642
ITEM 2 405 ADJ1=423 ADJ2=347
ITEM 9 693
*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAMINE 2
The white stones of the tower have been perfectly placed, making it appear
as if the entire building was carved out of a single rock. Not a single
line mars the surface of the smooth building.
*DESCRIPTION_END
VARIABLE shlade
IFPREVERB GO 0
   CLEARVERB
   IFVAR ORG ! 22
      IFCARRY 1908 -1
         ECHO OTHERS %P goes through the arch.
         ECHO PLAYER You go through the arch.
         MOVEGROUP 2643
         AFFECT 2643
         ECHO ALL %cThe guard standing inside the door nods to %N and says, "Welcome Associate %N."
       ELSE
         ECHO OTHERS %P goes through the arch.
         ECHO PLAYER You go through the arch.
         MOVEGROUP 2643
         AFFECT 2643
         ECHO ALL %cThe guard standing inside the door nods to %N and says, "Welcome %N."
       ENDIF
   ENDIF
   IFVAR ORG = 22
      IFVAR ORGRANK < 50
         ECHO OTHERS %P goes through the arch.
         ECHO PLAYER You go through the arch.
         MOVEGROUP 2643
        AFFECT 2643
         ECHO ALL %cThe guard standing inside the door bows to %N and says, "Welcome back, Initiate %N."
     ENDIF
      IFVAR ORGRANK < 99
         IFVAR ORGRANK > 49
            MOVEGROUP 2643
            ECHO OTHERS %P goes through the arch.
           ECHO PLAYER You go through the arch.
            AFFECT 2643
           ECHO ALL %cThe guard standing inside the door bows to %N and says, "Welcome back, Watcher %N."
         ENDIF
      ENDIF
      IFVAR ORGRANK < 199
         IFVAR ORGRANK > 98
            ECHO OTHERS %P goes through the arch.
            ECHO PLAYER You go through the arch.
            MOVEGROUP 2643
            AFFECT 2643
            ECHO ALL %cThe guard standing inside the door bows to %N and says, "Welcome back, Guardian %N."
         ENDIF
      ENDIF
      IFVAR ORGRANK < 5000
         IFVAR ORGRANK > 198
            ECHO OTHERS %P goes through the arch.
            ECHO PLAYER You go through the arch.
            MOVEGROUP 2643
            AFFECT 2643
            ECHO ALL %cThe guard standing inside the door bows deeply to %N and says, "Welcome back, Sentinel %N."
         ENDIF
      ENDIF
      IFVAR ORGRANK < 10000
         IFVAR ORGRANK > 5001
            ECHO OTHERS %P goes through the arch.
            ECHO PLAYER You go through the arch.
            MOVEGROUP 2643
            AFFECT 2643
            ECHO ALL %cThe guard standing inside the door bows deeply to %N and says, "Welcome back, High Sentinel %N."
         ENDIF
      ENDIF 
      IFVAR ORGRANK >= 10000
         ECHO OTHERS %P goes through the arch.
         ECHO PLAYER You go through the arch.
         MOVEGROUP 2643
         AFFECT 2643
         ECHO ALL %cThe guard standing inside the door bows deeply to %N and says, "Welcome back, Guildmistress %N."
      ENDIF
   ENDIF
ENDIF
IFVERB SMELL -1
  ECHO PLAYER The brisk smell of salt air cleanses your head.
  ECHO OTHERS %N faces the water and inhales deeply.
ENDIF
;
NUMBER 2642
NAME Eliditur Island, secluded beach
ASTRAL
CALL 33
DAY_LIGHT
*DESCRIPTION_START
Crystal clear blue waters gently lap against the pure white sand of this
secluded beach. This tiny slice of nature's beauty is protected from the
rest of the world by a ring of majestic trees that gently shelter the
lagoon from the ravages of harsh weather. Beautiful pink coral reefs are
visible under the water, where the erosion of the waves has caused
miniature castles to be formed from the delicate rocks.
*DESCRIPTION_END
ITEM 0 80 VAL2=2641
ITEM 1 1062 ADJ1=77 ADJ2=25
ITEM 2 413 ADJ1=347
ITEM 9 693
*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAMINE 2
The silken grains of sand stretch endlessly before your eyes, offering
inviting comfort and the captured warmth of sunrays.
*DESCRIPTION_END
IFVERB LISTEN -1
  ECHO PLAYER The gentle rushing of the surf soothes your tired nerves.
  ECHO OTHERS %N closes %h eyes sighs, letting tension flow away.
ENDIF
;
NUMBER 2643
NAME Eliditur Tower, foyer
ASTRAL
CALL 33
FIXED_LIGHT
*DESCRIPTION_START
The tangy scent of the sea flows through the archway, riding on the wings
of a slight breeze. The breeze freshens the entire entry chamber, causing
the fronds of the potted plants, that are arranged around a beautiful tile
mosaic in the floor, to wave gently. Stairways, leading up and down, offer
access to other parts of the tower. Above the archway, a plaque of bright
gleaming silver hangs. A guard stands at the archway.
*DESCRIPTION_END
ITEM 0 60 ADJ1=187 VAL2=2641
ITEM 1 547
ITEM 2 81 ADJ1=492 ADJ2=312 VAL2=2670
ITEM 3 1226 ADJ1=493 ADJ2=312 VAL2=2644
ITEM 4 400 ADJ1=292
ITEM 9 693
*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAMINE 1
Carefully arranged tiles portray a stylized silver rose with the words,
"The Eliditur Fellowship", above it. 
*DESCRIPTION_END
*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM READ 4
A long-stemmed red rose trails its way across the plaque, and encircles the
writing, "Drisanda, Hero of the Eliditur. He may be gone, but he will never
be forgotten." A deep gouge mark scratches its way across the surface of the
plaque.
*DESCRIPTION_END
IFENTRY -1
  ECHO ALL A lone guard snaps to attention.
ENDIF
IFSAY REPORT
  RANDOM DUMMY4 1 6 0
  IFVAR DUMMY4 = 1 
    ECHO ALL The guard snaps to attention and says, "Nothing to report!"
  ENDIF
  IFVAR DUMMY4 = 2
    ECHO ALL The guard snaps to attention and says, "There was a breach of the portal but we fought them back!"
  ENDIF
  IFVAR DUMMY4 = 3
    ECHO ALL The guard snaps to attention and says, "One of the Watcher's reported that he saw something deep inside the portal moving."
  ENDIF
  IFVAR DUMMY4 = 4
    ECHO ALL The guard narrows his eyes slightly, and says, "The King's guards tell us that Riesa has still not been recovered."
  ENDIF
  IFVAR DUMMY4 = 5
    ECHO ALL The guard says, "One of the guards reports he spotted Larissa leaving the island."
  ENDIF
  IFVAR DUMMY4 = 6
    ECHO ALL The guard snaps to attention and says, "The was a report about information regarding a library being located inside the tower."
  ENDIF
ENDIF
;
NUMBER 2644
NAME Eliditur Tower, basement
ASTRAL
CALL 33
FIXED_LIGHT
FORGE
*DESCRIPTION_START
Flickering flames from the fires within a forge cast their light over
the white walls of the chamber in a beautiful display of orange color.
The heat from the forge keeps the entire room at a comfortable working
temperature, just enough to break a sweat, but not enough to cause any
discomfort. Various smithing tools are neatly arrayed on the walls of
the chamber, their metallic sheen reflecting the fire.
*DESCRIPTION_END
ITEM 0 81 ADJ1=312 VAL2=2643
ITEM 1 1517
ITEM 2 1416
ITEM 9 693
;
NUMBER 2670
NAME Eliditur Tower, hall
ASTRAL
CALL 33
FIXED_LIGHT
*DESCRIPTION_START
Gracefully flowing stairways curve around the walls of the chamber, their
deeply polished marble steps seamlessly melding into the stone of the tower.
An arch, with carvings of intertwined silver roses across its face, leads
into a somewhat larger chamber to the west. A mural hangs on one wall, 
depicting a fierce looking drakin standing watch over the portal.
*DESCRIPTION_END
