*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAMINE 4
The steely-eyed drakin gazes back at you with a frightful intensity, his
eyes reflecting the depths of his commitment to the tenets of the Eliditur.
*DESCRIPTION_END
IFPREVERB PULL 4
  IFNOITEM 8
    NEWITEM 8 66 VAL2=2648
    ECHO PLAYER The mural swings out, revealing a doorway.
    ECHO OTHERS %N swings the mural out, revealing a doorway.
  ELSE
    ECHO PLAYER You tug on the mural, but it won't budge any further.
    ECHO OTHERS %N tugs on the mural, but it won't budge any further.
  ENDIF
ENDIF
IFPREVERB PUSH 4
  IFITEM 8
    REMOVEITEM -1
    ECHO PLAYER You push the mural back into place, sealing off the doorway.
    ECHO OTHERS %N pushes the mural back into place, sealing off the doorway.
  ELSE
    ECHO PLAYER You push futily on the mural.
    ECHO OTHERS %N pushes futily on the mural.
  ENDIF
ENDIF
IFPREVERB GO 0
  IFVAR ORG ! 22
    CLEARVERB
    ECHO ALL A guard steps in front of %N and says, "You may not pass this way unless escorted by a full member."
  ELSE
    ECHO ALL A guard waves %N through.
  ENDIF 
ENDIF
IFPREVERB GO 3
  CLEARVERB
    IFCARRY 1908 -1
      ECHO PLAYER You feel the wall accept your status as one of the Eliditur...an image of a beautiful rose fills your mind as you pass through the barrier.
      ECHO OTHERS %N's shape shimmers as %s passes through the wall...
      MOVEGROUP 2271
      AFFECT 2271
      ECHO OTHERS %P arrives through the wall.
      ELSE
      ECHO PLAYER Your face bounces off the wall.
      ECHO OTHERS %N's face bounces off the wall.
    ENDIF
ENDIF
