NUMBER 2271
NAME Eliditur Island, jungle
ASTRAL
CALL 33
OBSCURED_DAY_LIGHT
*DESCRIPTION_START
Wildly growing trees and bushes overwhelm the surroundings in a cornucopia
of colors and smells. Lush, green vines snake up the ivory wall of the
Eliditur tower to the south, while bushes line a path to the north. Your
senses reel with pleasure as you take in the surroundings, but you also
realize that not a single animal inhabits this serene place, almost as if
they were in awe of the jungle.
*DESCRIPTION_END
EXIT N 2272
ITEM 0 420
ITEM 9 693
*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAMINE 0
The vines can't hide the magical quality of the wall, and you feel somewhat
reassured that it offers entrance to the relative safety of the Eliditur
tower.
*DESCRIPTION_END
IFVERB LISTEN -1
  ECHO PLAYER The only sound is that of your own breathing, and the soft breeze that rustles the surrounding leaves.
ENDIF
IFVERB SMELL -1
  ECHO PLAYER A startling number of pleasant smells, from the surrounding foliage, fills your nostrils.
  ECHO OTHERS %N takes a deep breath and smiles pleasantly.
ENDIF
IFPREVERB GO 0
  CLEARVERB
   ECHO PLAYER You pass through the wall.
   ECHO OTHERS %P passes through the vine-covered wall.
   MOVEGROUP 2670
   AFFECT 2670
   ECHO OTHERS %P arrives through the wall.
ENDIF
;
NUMBER 2272
NAME Eliditur Island, portal
ASTRAL
CALL 33
OBSCURED_DAY_LIGHT
*DESCRIPTION_START
The foliage shrinks back from the blackened ground here. Raw power of
immense proportions crackles around the solitary arch that sits in the
center of the charred clearing. Within the arch is a red field with
black and red lights streaking throughout. Skeletons and rusted weapons
litter the ground, remnants of the battles that raged here in times gone
by. The blood that coats the ground in various spots remain as a solemn
memorial to those who have given their lives in this very spot.
*DESCRIPTION_END
EXIT S 2271
ITEM 0 60
ITEM 9 693
