VARIABLE severian
IFVERB LISTEN -1
  ECHO PLAYER The extreme silence adds to the solemnity of this place.
ENDIF
IFVERB SMELL -1
  ECHO PLAYER The smell of blood and smoke reminds you of the battles that have been fought here.
ENDIF
IFPREVERB LOOK 0
  CLEARVERB
    ECHO PLAYER Nine holes mark the surface of the impressive arch. The holes have been carefully placed so as not to mar the effect of the carvings running the length of the stone face. The carvings are horrid symbols of pain and death, even more terrible for their alieness...You notice that three of the holes are filled with immovable black gems that gleam with an evil of their own...
      IFVAR ORG = 22
        ECHO PLAYER The field opens slightly and allows you a view of a blasted, reddish world upon which demons walk. You sense that they are staring directly at you...they begin to run towards you, their skin oozing blood and smoking from the acidic rain that splatters down onto them...a moment before they reach you, you manage to tear your gaze away...and the rift within the arch shuts...
        ECHO OTHERS %N gasps softly, as a wail of unimaginable rage comes from the arch...
      ENDIF
ENDIF
IFVERB RECALL -1
  IFVAR ORG = 22
    ECHO PLAYER You stand before the arch that stands in two worlds, that of your and that of the evil demon race, the Tharkon. Here, in this spot, is where the drakin warrior, Parok, stood against the forces of evil, valiantly giving his life so that others may live. It is here where Derinius called upon his own magics and the glory of Rorin to seal the denizens of Ngyal Ag into their own world. Here...history lives...here is the reason you are...Eliditur.
  ENDIF
ENDIF
IFPREVERB2 PUT 0
  CLEARVERB
  IFVAR severian = 1
   IFVAR ORG = 22
    IFVAR FLAG1 = 0
     IFVAR ARCHNUM = 118
      REMOVEITEM -1
      ECHO PLAYER You place the ruby into one of the darkness oozing cracks on the arch...
      ECHO OTHERS %N places a ruby into one of the darkness oozing cracks on the arch...
      EQUAL FLAG1 1
      PLREVENT 7
      CONTPLREVENT
       IFVAR FLAG1 ! 3
         ECHO PLAYER Your attempt has failed! Another Zharkier lumbers forth from within the arch!
         ECHO OTHERS %N's attempt has failed! Another Zharkier lumbers forth from within the arch!
         GENMON 192
         EQUAL FLAG1 0
       ENDIF
     ENDIF
    ENDIF
   ENDIF
  ENDIF
ENDIF
IFSAY The_power_of_Eliditur_I_call_forth!
  IFVAR FLAG1 = 1
    ECHO PLAYER You feel the power of the Eliditur flow through your body, making you dizzy with its power.
    ECHO OTHERS The power of the Eliditur flows through %N, making %i glow with a dazzling silvery light!
