*DESCRIPTION_START
Standing on the small ledge, you can see for hundreds of miles around. A most
beautiful view of a deep blue ocean stretches across your field of view, along
with the small jungle on the island below. The only thing separating you from
a several hundred foot fall is a simple black metal railing. Oddly, there
seems to be a blue shimmering coming from across the ocean, but it may simply
be a trick of the eye, though you aren't sure how to explain the eerie silence
that comes from the ocean.
