NUMBER 2647
NAME Eliditur Tower, top
ASTRAL
DAY_LIGHT
*DESCRIPTION_START
Neatly arranged across the length of the tower roof is a small garden with
sights, sounds and smells that bring whoever enters here a deep sense of
peace. The bushes and trees, all laden with sweet-smelling flowers and ripe
fruits, spiral inwards towards a circular pool of shimmering water. White
marble benches are placed around the pool, directly underneath some
tall trees that offer shade from the heat of the day-time sun. A cleverly
hidden stairway leads back down to the interior of the tower.
*DESCRIPTION_END
